"Recent clipboard" = "最近剪貼板";
"Everything you copy lands here. Right-click any row to save it as a cutling." = "你複製的所有內容都會到這裡。在任一列上按右鍵即可將其儲存為剪切片段。";
"Wipe the list" = "清空列表";
"Empties your recent clipboard. Saved cutlings stay put." = "清空你最近的剪貼板。已儲存的剪切片段保持不變。";
"Rebind the hotkey, toggle clipboard capture, and manage iCloud sync." = "重新指定快速鍵、切換剪貼板擷取，並管理 iCloud 同步。";
"Undo deletes" = "復原刪除";
"Deleted cutlings stay here for 30 days. Restore them or empty for good." = "刪除的剪切片段在這裡保留 30 天。可回復它們，亦可永久清空。";
"Tap here to select multiple cutlings, reorder them, or restore recently deleted ones." = "點一下此處可選擇多個剪切片段、重新排序，或回復最近刪除的項目。";
"Long-press a cutling" = "長按剪切片段";
"Hold any card for quick actions: copy, edit, share, or delete." = "按住任一張卡片以使用快速操作：複製、編輯、分享或刪除。";
"Drag to select" = "拖移以選擇";
"Swipe across cards to select a range. Swipe back over them to deselect." = "在卡片上滑動以選擇範圍。反向滑動可取消選擇。";
"Smart field matching" = "智慧型欄位比對";
"Cutling spots email, URL, phone, and address fields, then floats matching snippets to the top of the keyboard." = "剪切片段會偵測電子郵件、URL、電話和地址欄位，並將相符的片段放到鍵盤頂部。";
"Create a new cutling" = "建立新的剪切片段";
"Save text or image snippets you'll reuse from any app." = "儲存你會在任何 App 中重複使用的文字或圖片片段。";

/* MARK: - Welcome Window (macOS first launch) */
"Welcome to Cutling" = "歡迎使用剪切片段";
"Your clipboard, organised." = "井然有序的剪貼板。";
"Save the snippets, images, and links you reuse. Capture everything you copy. Paste anywhere with one shortcut." = "儲存你常用的片段、圖片和連結。每次複製的內容都會被記錄下來，只需一個快捷鍵即可貼上到任何地方。";
"Look up. Cutling lives in your menu bar" = "請看螢幕上方，剪切片段就在選單列中";
"The clipboard icon at the top of your screen opens Cutling any time. Click it to see your saved cutlings and recent clipboard history." = "螢幕上方的剪貼板圖示可隨時開啟剪切片段。點一下即可查看已儲存的剪切片段和最近的剪貼板歷史。";
"Summon Cutling from anywhere" = "隨時隨地呼叫剪切片段";
"Press ⌘⇧V from any app to open a floating picker at your cursor. Pick a cutling and it's ready to paste, no menu bar trip required." = "在任何 App 中按下 ⌘⇧V，即可在游標處開啟浮動選擇器。選擇一個剪切片段後即可立即貼上，無需前往選單列。";
"Rebind it later in Settings → Hotkey." = "你可以稍後在「設定 → 快捷鍵」中重新指定。";
"Almost there" = "就快好了";
"You're all set" = "全部就緒";
"Two quick permissions so Cutling can work the way you'd expect. You can change either later in Settings." = "只需兩個簡單的權限，剪切片段就能如你所願地運作。兩者都可以稍後在設定中變更。";
"Launch at login" = "登入時啟動";
"Open Cutling automatically when you sign in." = "登入時自動開啟剪切片段。";
"Accessibility access" = "輔助使用權限";
"Granted. Cutling can paste directly into other apps." = "已授予。剪切片段可直接貼上至其他 App。";
"Lets Cutling paste a cutling straight into the app you were using." = "讓剪切片段可以直接把內容貼到你正在使用的 App 中。";
"Grant" = "授予權限";
"You can skip Accessibility and grant it later from Settings → Paste." = "你可以跳過輔助使用，稍後在「設定 → 貼上」中授予。";


